        },
        "text_mEJtMk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most wicking fabrics dry sweat so fast that your body never benefits from it. Delta does the opposite: it disperses moisture across the jersey to maximize evaporative cooling.Two unique yarns make it happen. Tencel™ lyocell (hydrophilic) pulls sweat away from your skin. Polyester (hydrophobic) spreads it across the surface where airflow accelerates evaporation. The technical knit's texturing optimizes airflow, so your body's cooling system works harder for you.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
