        },
        "text_MjXHzE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Evaporative cooling. </strong>Delta disperses sweat to boost your body's natural cooling, rather than drying it before it can do its job.</p><p><strong>Reduced wet-cling. </strong>Elevated touch-points lift the fabric off your skin, preventing that soggy, stuck-to-your-back feeling.</p><p><strong>Naturally odor-resistant. </strong>Tencel lyocell fibers reduce odor buildup, so the Habanero stays fresher longer between washes.</p><p><strong>Lightweight and breathable. </strong>Built for high-heat conditions with continuous airflow and heat dissipation.</p><p><strong>Deadstock fabric.</strong>Made from Polartec Delta that never made it to the cutting table. We only get one shot with deadstock. When it's gone, it's gone. Made in USA.</p>",
